particular, we insist that papers should (1) be written for a wide =
audience and
(2) focus on the problematic, successful, etc. ontological aspects. =
Following
the previous FOMI editions, we are considering publishing the =
proceedings of
the workshop in the FAIA series (IOS Press) or as a special issue of
&quot;Applied Ontology&quot;.<o:p></o:p></span></font></p>

